  "title": "Body Therapist Reflexologist Supervisor / Manager",
  "description": "<p>For this Body Therapist Reflexologist Supervisor/ Manager, the role must understand how the body's muscles interact and know how to treat specific body parts. Body Therapist Reflexologist Supervisor/ Manager works one-on-one with clients, and manages the team so interpersonal skills and professionalism are essential.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>聘请足疗/按摩治疗师 Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>1) Massages customers and administers other body conditioning treatments like alcohol, lubricants, or other rubbing compounds for hygienic or remedial purposes.</p>\n<p>2) Massages body and foot, using such techniques as kneading, rubbing, and stroking flesh, to stimulate blood circulation, relax contracted muscles, facilitate the elimination of toxicity, or relieve other conditions, using hands or tools.</p>\n<p>3) Administers TCM treatments or water treatments at the request of the customer.</p>\n<p>4) May give directions to clients in activities, such as reducing or remedial exercises.</p>\n<p>5) May examine the client and recommend body conditioning activities or treatments.</p>\n<p>6) Able to record treatments furnished to customers.</p>\n<p>7) Able to supervise and manage the team.</p>\n<p>8) Maintains staff by recruiting, selecting, orienting, and training employees.</p>\n<p>9) Oversee the company operation and staffs duties</p>\n<p>10) Report to the director the company's operations and updates.</p>\n<p>Prefer with relevant Diploma qualification &amp; at least 3 years experience</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Looking Body Therapist Reflexologist Supervisor or Manager role</p>\n<p>Able to commit on 6 days per week</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Able to do overtime and might need to do long hours</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- 工作经验：有3年或以上工作经验，</p>\n<p>- 上班时间：10:00-22:00，（包括了午餐和晚餐的时间），</p>\n<p>- 良好的个人卫生习卫生习惯</p>\n<p>- 鉴于按摩需要一定的体力</p>",
